description: Warren Rocko is a member of the Fairy Tail Guild. Although he may not look it, he is classified as one of the more powerful wizards in the guild, and he has gone on a huge number of jobs alone. His fear of heights causes him many problems. At one point he took a girl on a date, but as they were crossing a bridge, his mental shouts of "Help, save me!!! I`m scared!!!" were heard by everyone in the town.
name: Warren Rocko
